local Manager = s_WordDictionaryDatabase; Manager.allwords["denial"]={"denial","[dɪ'naɪ(ə)l]","[dɪ'naɪəl]","n.否认",'n.否认,拒绝','An opinion or a doctrine at variance with established religious beliefs, especially dissension from or denial of Roman Catholic dogma by a professed believer or baptized church member.','异端学说与已得到承认的宗教信仰相矛盾的观点或学说，尤指已立誓信教或受过洗礼的教徒对罗马天主教教义的异议或否认','His reply approaches to a denial.','他的回答几乎等于拒绝。'}
